findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function eject() uses a loop to iterate through userDepositsForEject array, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters and execute internal functions, posing a high risk of manipulation.
